</link><description>三位知情人士称，英伟达正在为中国市场开发一款新的旗舰人工智能芯片，该芯片将与美国当前的出口管制兼容。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 04:02:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-preparing-version-new-flaghip-ai-chip-chinese-market-sources-say-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国菲律宾大使馆要求回应针对新冠疫苗的宣传</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-philippines-embassy-demands-answers-propaganda-against-covid-vaccine-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国驻菲律宾大使馆周一表示，美国应尽快就其针对中国COVID-19疫苗的虚假宣传向菲律宾人民作出解释。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/chinas-philippines-embassy-demands-answers-propaganda-against-covid-vaccine-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>渣打银行关联的中国渤海银行寻求处置 40 亿美元不良贷款</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-linked-china-bohai-seeks-dispose-4-bln-bad-loans-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国渤海银行周一表示，由于中国经济步履蹒跚和房地产行业问题日益严重，迫使银行处置不良资产，该银行正计划出售价值290亿元人民币（合39.9亿美元）的不良贷款。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:33:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/stanchart-linked-china-bohai-seeks-dispose-4-bln-bad-loans-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国下调短期和长期利率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cuts-short-long-term-rates-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国周一将短期和长期利率下调 10 个基点，央行表示旨在支持经济增长。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:17:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-cuts-short-long-term-rates-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>台湾开始年度军事演习 旨在紧密模拟实战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-starts-annual-war-games-aiming-closely-mimic-actual-combat-2024-07-22/</link><description>台湾一年一度的汉光兵棋周一开始，今年的目标是尽可能接近实战，没有剧本，模拟如何击退中国的进攻。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 02:17:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-starts-annual-war-games-aiming-closely-mimic-actual-combat-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>失火油轮被海岸警卫队扣留后进入马来西亚码头区</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fire-hit-oil-tanker-enters-malaysia-fpso-bertam-terminal-area-data-shows-2024-07-22/</link><description>伦敦证券交易所集团 (LSEG) 和 Kpler 的航运数据显示，一艘上周在新加坡附近发生碰撞的油轮在周日被地方当局拦截后，于周一早上进入马来西亚 Bertam 浮动油码头区域。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:36:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/fire-hit-oil-tanker-enters-malaysia-fpso-bertam-terminal-area-data-shows-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车与大众成立项目公司推出新的电动汽车架构</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-volkswagen-set-up-project-house-roll-out-new-ev-architecture-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国电动汽车（EV）制造商小鹏汽车周一表示，已与德国汽车制造商大众汽车公司合作建立了工程师项目室，以加快新电动汽车架构的开发进程。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 01:03:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-volkswagen-set-up-project-house-roll-out-new-ev-architecture-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着拜登结束连任竞选，美元走软；降息后人民币走弱</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-biden-ends-reelection-bid-yuan-steady-after-rate-cut-2024-07-22/</link><description>美元周一小幅下跌，因投资者评估美国总统乔·拜登决定结束连任竞选并为另一位民主党人挑战唐纳德·特朗普扫清道路的影响。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:48:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/dollar-eases-biden-ends-reelection-bid-yuan-steady-after-rate-cut-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>部长表示，菲律宾正在考虑与法国、加拿大和新西兰签署防务协定</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-eyes-defence-pacts-with-france-canada-nz-minister-says-2024-07-22/</link><description>菲律宾国防部长周一表示，菲律宾正在寻求与加拿大、法国、新西兰和其他国家达成互惠的部队准入协议。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:43:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-eyes-defence-pacts-with-france-canada-nz-minister-says-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国出人意料地下调关键利率以支持脆弱的经济</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-cuts-short-term-policy-rate-2024-07-22/</link><description>中国周一降低了关键的短期政策利率和基准贷款利率，以促进世界第二大经济体的增长，令市场感到意外。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:26:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/china-central-bank-cuts-short-term-policy-rate-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>随着中国降息，亚洲股市下滑；拜登退到一边</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-22/</link><description>亚洲股市周一再次下跌，中国央行意外降息几乎没有带来什么提振，而在美国总统乔·拜登决定退出竞选后，华尔街期货走强。</description><pubDate>Mon, 22 Jul 2024 00:22:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-07-22/</guid></item><item><title>中国对冲基金准备迎接严厉新规定带来的剧变</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-hedge-funds-brace-upheaval-tough-new-rules-2024-07-21/</link><description>中国价值7150亿美元的对冲基金行业正面临下个月生效的严格监管带来的新压力，迫使一些投资公司向白衣骑士寻求新资金，甚至关门歇业。</description><pubDate>Sun, 21 Jul 2024 23:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/china-hedge-funds-brace-upheaval-tough-new-rules-2024-07-21/</guid></item></channel></rss>